# =============================================================================
# This is a PUBLIC repo. Real/proprietary data must NOT be committed here.
# Keep the real data OUTSIDE this repo (see portal/data_loader.py _private_data_root):
#   1. set $PORTAL_DATA_DIR to a private folder, or
#   2. clone your private data repo as a sibling folder named  dashboard-data
# The bundled sample under accuracy_tables/ + portal/calculators/*.csv stays
# tracked on purpose so the public code still runs as a demo.
# =============================================================================

# Private data repo, if ever cloned/placed INSIDE this repo tree by mistake
/dashboard-data/
dashboard-data/

# Streamlit secrets / any dotenv files (may hold PORTAL_DATA_DIR or credentials)
.streamlit/secrets.toml
*.env
.env
.env.*

# One-time seed output: temporary login passwords written by portal/seed_users.py.
# NEVER commit — delete after the first login/rotation.
.streamlit/seed_credentials.txt
*.local

# Python caches / build junk
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
